value:
Everybody keeps showering me with
gifts. I guess I'm pretty popular!

The New Year's parties in Askr make
the ones in the Deeprealms look
super small.

I went to a temple earlier, and guess
what? The statues there looked just
like me! I wonder if they're kitsune...

I tried to get Velouria to come out of
her room and play, but nope! Not
even for New Year's! Laaame!

I'm so glad my daddy likes this New
Year's kimono. He can sometimes be
a little bit picky about clothes!

Hi! Hehe! Happy New Year! I'm from
$Nf's castle!

I've gotten lots stronger since last
year. You'll see!

It may be a whole new year, but
mochi and playtime never get old!
Don't let my cute outfit get dirty, OK?

Aww, you got me a gift for New
Year's? Yay! Thank you!

Hi! I'm Selkie and I'm a kitsune! Wait,
I was supposed to tell you something
else. Oh yeah! Happy New Year!

Thanks for getting me this super-cute
outfit, $Nu!$k$pIt really goes well with my ears and
tail. I love it so much!$k$pNew Year's is great, but sometimes
I wonder why we can't just party and
play like this all the time.$k$pI guess we've gotta bring peace to
Askr and all that first though, huh?
That way everyone can relax!$k$pOK, that does it! I'm gonna beat up
all the bad guys, so the next New
Year's party doesn't have to end!
(Exertion)
Here I go!
Urgh...
Ouch!
What a fun new year!
Happy new ears!
Did YOU eat my mochi!?
Let's play! Let's play!
Too...much...mochi.
Hahaha!
Happy New Year!
Hi! Let's celebrate the new year with some play time!
Want to know what's in this gourd? It's not for kids, so NOTHING! *laughs*
*Yawn* Can I please have some pats? All that food made me sleepy...
I have the best daddy ever! He gave me a New Year's gift!
Your New Year's resolution is to give me lots and lots of snuggles and pats this year, okay?
Does this kimono look cute on me? Hehe, of course it does! Now let's go on an adventure!
Hooray!
Play time?
Lookin' good!
